}
```

**Technology Notes**:
- Next.js 15 App Router (static page by default)
- React 19 Server Components (no 'use client' directive)
- Metadata API for SEO
- JSON-LD structured data for search engines
- Suspense for progressive enhancement

**Best Practices**:
- Static generation for marketing pages (fastest performance)
- Open Graph tags for social sharing
- Canonical URLs to prevent duplicate content
- Structured data (JSON-LD) for rich search results
- Mobile-responsive design

