## VI. SUMMARY

This Frontend Page Components Specialist document provides comprehensive guidance for implementing the Pages Layer in Next.js 15 applications using Feature-Sliced Design (FSD). The specialist covers:

- **12+ Detailed Pattern Implementations**: From Pattern 10.1 (Home Page) to Pattern 10.25 (Workflow List)
- **Complete TypeScript Code Examples**: Production-ready implementations
- **Vietnamese Legal Domain Context**: Tailored for StarX4CRM use case
- **Next.js 15 Best Practices**: App Router, Server Components, Suspense
- **Performance Optimization**: Caching strategies, parallel loading, progressive rendering
- **Security Considerations**: Authentication, authorization, data protection

The patterns follow Next.js 15.3.0 conventions with React 19 and TypeScript 5 strict mode, providing a scalable foundation for building complex page-based applications.

